{{year-header}}
==January==
* '''[[13 January|13]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] sends [[Letter to Elizabeth Jones|a letter to Elizabeth Jones]].
==February==
* '''[[9 February|9]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[letter 222a]].
* '''[[12 February|12]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[letter 222b]].
* '''[[29 February|29]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[letter 222c]].
==March==
* '''[[1 March|1]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[letter 222d]].
* '''[[17 March|17]]''' - [[Jef Murray]] is born.
==April==
* '''[[4 April|4]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[letter 222e]].
* '''[[4 April|4]]''' - [[Hugo Weaving]], who would play [[Elrond]] in [[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|''The Lord of the Rings'' (film series)]], is born.
==May==
* '''[[5 May|5]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[letter 222f]].
* '''?''' - [[Triode 18|''Triode'' 18]], including [[Letter to the editor of Triode|a letter by J.R.R. Tolkien]], is published.
==July==
* '''[[7 July|7]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]] writes [[Letter to H.W. Donner|a letter]] to [[H.W. Donner]]. 
* '''[[9 July|9]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]] has a formal dinner in [[Cambridge]].
* '''[[31 July|31]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[letter 223]].
==September==
* '''[[4 September|4]]''' - [[The Fellowship of the Ring (fangroup)|The Fellowship of the Ring]] becomes formally constituted.
* '''[[12 September|12]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[letter 224]].
* '''[[23 September|23]]''' - [[Jason Carter]], who would voice [[Glorfindel]] in ''[[EA's The Battle for Middle-earth II]]'' and ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Battle for Middle-earth II: The Rise of the Witch-king|The Rise of the Witch-king]]'', is born.
==October==
* '''[[25 October|25]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] seeks (through his secretary [[Elisabeth Lumsden]]) to publish "a sort of satirical fantasy") believed to be ''[[The End of Bovadium]]'' in the magazine ''[[Wikipedia:Time and Tide (magazine)|Time and Tide]]''.
==December==
* '''[[10 December|10]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[letter 225]].
* '''[[14 December|14]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] draws [[:File:J.R.R. Tolkien - Idril Celebrindal heraldic device (I).jpg|Idril Celebrindal's heraldic device]].
* '''[[31 December|31]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] writes [[letter 226]].
==?==
* '''?''' - [[I.L. Gordon]] publishes an edition of the [[Old English]] poem ''[[The Seafarer (I.L. Gordon)|The Seafarer]]'', to which [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] contributed.
* '''?''' - ''[[The Four Loves]]'', a book by [[C.S. Lewis]] with a reference to [[J.R.R. Tolkien]], is published.
* '''?''' - Actor [[Peter Hambleton]] is born.
